  "finalSubmissionGuidelines": "<p dir=\"ltr\">Kindly make sure that before uploading your submission, it:</p>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li dir=\"ltr\">\n\t<p dir=\"ltr\">Meets the specification documents shared</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir=\"ltr\">\n\t<p dir=\"ltr\">Passes all the lint checks using the ESLint rules that we mentioned</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir=\"ltr\">\n\t<p dir=\"ltr\">Includes Unit Tests. POSTMAN extension based imports are NOT allowed</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir=\"ltr\">\n\t<p dir=\"ltr\">Implements all the endpoints requested</p>\n\t</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><br />\nOnce you are ready, create a .zip file of the submission and upload this through the Submit and Review tool for this contest.</p>\n",
